Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.15,0:41:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.63,0:41:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's not thinking you can think later, but not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.07,0:42:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have time to think now because the witness observer is automatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.80,0:42:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The easiest way to enlightenment is to withdraw from identifying with the content of consciousness and realize, how do I even know what's going on in consciousness because of the witness observer?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.55,0:42:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So you withdraw from the content to the witness observer, and that takes you right in eventually to consciousness itself.
